text:
Oh, Tenka.
You came at just the right time.

The data from the recent shoot just came in.
Want to take a look?

Oh... there are also
photos of Naa-chan and Chiyuki-san...!

When we're lined up like this...
it looks... really nice, doesn't it...!
it does look good, doesn't it, ALSTROEMERIA?

During the shoot, Tenka...
wasn't feeling very confident...

But when the three of us are together...
feel completely confident...!
